divs: Sighting Detailswe took a picture of a plane that looked like a missile and a few days later loaded it on the computer.we were amazed to see what looked like a bunch of smaller type objects going in the opposite direction of the plane missile.we have the photo and it should be looked at because it is very strange and we are not sure what it is. note at another date around late summer we heard a small plane revving up his motor and my wife saw what we belive was a thing called a rod but it was very big from her description, i also heard the plane that seemed to be in distress... motor revivng.. my wife said she thought they were going to collide.we would like somebady to see this photo to see if its anything that should be investigated.please let us know what you think .we are responsible people in our early 60s and have seen plenty of unusual things this is the first time we have said anything because people think your crazy.best regards r.j. romano
Summary: have photo looks like missile with pastel color objects around it many of them
